# People Center — runs against the CGOPS Platform Supabase project (Phase A
# lift-and-shift; see docs/RUNBOOK_CGOPS_LIFT_AND_SHIFT.md).
# Copy to .env and fill in values (CGOPS dashboard → Settings → API).
# Server-side secrets (service role key) never go here.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://<CGOPS_PROJECT_REF>.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# CGOPS Platform URL — the front door. People Center has no standalone login:
# unauthenticated visits redirect here, and CGOPS launches People Center back
# with the SSO handoff fragment (#cgops_sso=1&access_token=...&refresh_token=...).
VITE_CGOPS_URL=
